 stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package w-5 h-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg></div><div><div class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-900\">Midwest</div><div class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-500\">Shipment Company</div></div></a><div class=\"hidden flex-1 items-center justify-center md:flex\"><nav class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6\"><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-[0.8rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-700 transition hover:text-brand-500\" href=\"/track\">Track Parcel</a></nav></div><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 md:flex\"><a class=\"rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-900 transition hover:border-brand-400 hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/track\">Track Package</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-brand-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-white transition hover:bg-brand-400\" href=\"/contact\">Get Quote</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-3 text-white transition hover:bg-white/10 md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-navy-950 text-white\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,_rgba(56,189,248,0.18),_transparent_18%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,_rgba(59,130,246,0.16),_transparent_28%)]\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-sky-300\">Midwest Shipment</p><h1 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl\">Fast freight movement across air, sea and road.</h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-2xl text-slate-200 leading-8\">Real-time tracking, premium handling, and logistics support built for modern supply chains.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-sky-400\" href=\"/track\">Track your shipment</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/20\" href=\"/services\">View services</a></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-300\">Next-day delivery</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">1-2 days</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-300\">Covered routes</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">160+ countries</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-300\">Support</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-white\">24/7 logistics care</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-sky-500 text-white\">Fast freight movement across air, sea and road.</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-white/10 text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/20\">End-to-end warehousing and delivery solutions.</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-white/10 text-slate-200 hover:bg-white/20\">Premium cargo care for urgent and sensitive loads.</button></div></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 shadow-2xl\"><img src=\"/images/hero-poster.png\" alt=\"Fast freight movement across air, sea and road.\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950/95 to-transparent p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-sky-300\">Featured route</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Reliable pickup and delivery for every lane.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-20 pt-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-xl\"><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-600\">Reliable courier services</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl\">A professional shipping experience built for brands and enterprise logistics.</h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-slate-600 leading-8\">Midwest Shipment makes your cargo movement look premium from pickup through delivery. Our service model mirrors the consistency of top courier brands while using your own distinctive imagery.</p><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Express shipping</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">Next-day delivery on select routes.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Trusted operations</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">Track packages with real-time updates and alerts.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-500\" href=\"/track\">Track Shipment</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-100\" href=\"/contact\">Request a quote</a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-xl\"><img src=\"/images/service-right-1.jpg\" alt=\"Courier delivery\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-600\">Track with confidence</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl\">One dashboard for every package and every lane.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 leading-8\">Enter your tracking code below to get live updates, delivery estimates, and shipment details from our carrier network.</p><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr]\"><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Enter tracking number\" class=\"w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-4 text-slate-900 placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-brand-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-500/20\"/><button class=\"inline-flex min-w-[170px] items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-600 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-brand-500\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search mr-2 h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg>Track Now</button></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Delivered packages</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">2.1M+</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Trusted partners</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">500+</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Countries covered</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">160+</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-slate-500\">Customer rating</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900\">4.9/5</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-20 pt-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-xl\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center\"><div><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-600\">Why choose Midwest</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl\">Premium parcel care for every stage of your delivery.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-8\">We combine high-touch customer service, secure handling, and intelligent routing so your shipments arrive on time with full visibility.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Accelerated dispatch</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Intelligent routing and proactive coordination to move shipments faster.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Safe, compliant cargo</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Insured, regulated handling for sensitive and high-value deliveries.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Enterprise visibility</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Live tracking and transparent updates for every shipment milestone.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-truck h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 18V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v11a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 18H9\"></path><path d=\"M19 18h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3.65a1 1 0 0 0-.22-.624l-3.48-4.35A1 1 0 0 0 17.52 8H14\"></path><circle cx=\"17\" cy=\"18\" r=\"2\"></circle><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"18\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Air &amp; Road Freight</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Seamless global freight movement with fast, efficient air and ground logistics.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-ship h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 10.189V14\"></path><path d=\"M12 2v3\"></path><path d=\"M19 13V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6\"></path><path d=\"M19.38 20A11.6 11.6 0 0 0 21 14l-8.188-3.639a2 2 0 0 0-1.624 0L3 14a11.6 11.6 0 0 0 2.81 7.76\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1s1.2 1 2.5 1c2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Ocean Freight</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Reliable FCL and LCL ocean shipping supported by full customs and port management.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-warehouse h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 21V10a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v11\"></path><path d=\"M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 1.132-1.803l7.95-3.974a2 2 0 0 1 1.837 0l7.948 3.974A2 2 0 0 1 22 8z\"></path><path d=\"M6 13h12\"></path><path d=\"M6 17h12\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Warehousing</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Smart storage solutions with secure facilities and inventory visibility.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Global Coverage</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">A worldwide carrier network built for cross-border shipments and regional distribution.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Secure Logistics</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Protected handling for sensitive cargo, documents, and high-value freight.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-400/30\"><div class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 text-brand-600\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Fulfillment &amp; Packaging</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600 leading-7\">Custom packaging, consolidation, and insured delivery for every shipment.</p></div></div></section></main><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-24 pt-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-12 text-center\"><p class=\"section-subtitle text-brand-400\">Trusted by international partners</p><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl\">Customer testimonials from premium logistics clients</h2></div><div class=\"swiper space-y-8 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"swiper-wrapper\"><div class=\"swiper-slide\"><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border